## Features

- **Dual-model scoring** — BERT semantic similarity (60%) + TF-IDF keyword matching (40%)
- **Multi-format parsing** — PDF and DOCX resume upload support
- **Batch processing** — Upload 50+ resumes at once via drag-and-drop
- **NER extraction** — Auto-extract candidate name, organisations, skills, and dates (spaCy)
- **Shortlist threshold** — Configurable cutoff score (default: 0.65)
- **SHAP explainability** — See the top keywords that drove each candidate's score
- **CSV export** — Download the ranked shortlist with one click
- **JWT authentication** — Secure HR-only access with token-based auth
- **REST API** — All features accessible programmatically via FastAPI
- **Docker ready** — One-command deployment with `docker compose up`

